{"tid":1080228,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[死神又來了]查比高恩斯空難 生還記者心臟病發逝世","createTime":"2019-03-27T12:45:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T12:59:12.000Z","uid":187960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"821e256041b893b779376232eabc17a485dfb7e0","tid":1080228,"uid":187960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T12:45:17.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=5mmA4sQKuQaI7%2FjJJ4WTlw0QAWntaMGUWBfwPSaCbl8%3D&h=af2a1adb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】查比高恩斯證實，2016年空難生還者之一，在電台任職記者的軒素於周二因心臟病發逝世，終年45歲。<br />\n據巴西《環球電視網》報道，軒素（Rafael Henzel）在巴西南部城市沙佩科踢足球時暈倒，儘管及時被送往醫院，但他不久後已證實死亡。軒素在查比高恩斯空難中恢復過來後已回到了他的電台工作，在當地是備受尊重的人物。 查比高恩斯在官方網表示，「在他輝煌的生平中，拉斐爾講述了查比高恩斯的故事。他是球會重建的象徵，這綠白色的球會將永遠懷念他。」 2016年11月28日，查比高恩斯本來作客南美球會盃決賽對哥倫比亞的國民體育會，卻被突如其來的空難徹底摧毀，77名乘客中有71人身亡，機上只有6人生還，當中包括隨隊出發的記者軒素。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a9316ba60617a83022580d8536be16a997aabae","tid":1080228,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T12:57:47.000Z","msg":"一個都不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a583fc27888af8d33348335f51dfcc836fdd38c9","tid":1080228,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T12:59:12.000Z","msg":"閻王要你三更死...."}]}